trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.ReplicationCursor" /> class represents a replication operation occurrence.
trans-unit.target: <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.ReplicationCursor" /> 類別表示複寫作業的發生。

trans-unit.source: Gets the time of the last successful replication synchronization with the replication source server.
trans-unit.target: 取得上一次與複寫來源伺服器複寫同步處理成功的時間。

trans-unit.source: The time at which the last successful replication synchronization occurred.
trans-unit.target: 上一次發生成功的複寫同步處理之時間。

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.ReplicationCursor.LastSuccessfulSyncTime%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType> indicates the time when this domain controller last synchronized to changes for this partition on the source directory system agent (DSA).
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.ReplicationCursor.LastSuccessfulSyncTime%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType>表示的時間，當此網域控制站上次同步處理來源目錄系統代理程式 (DSA) 上的這個資料分割的變更。

trans-unit.source: This property is not supported on [!INCLUDE[Win2kFamily](~/includes/win2kfamily-md.md)].
Gets the name of the partition to which this replication operation was applied.
trans-unit.target: 取得套用此複寫作業的磁碟分割名稱。

trans-unit.source: The name of the partition represented by this replication cursor.
trans-unit.target: 這個複寫資料指標 (Cursor) 所表示的磁碟分割名稱。

trans-unit.source: Gets the invocation identifier of the replication source server.
trans-unit.target: 取得複寫來源伺服器的引動過程識別項。

trans-unit.source: The invocation identifier of the replication source server
trans-unit.target: 複寫來源伺服器的引動過程識別項。

trans-unit.source: Gets the name of the replication source server.
trans-unit.target: 取得複寫來源伺服器的名稱。

trans-unit.source: The name of the replication source server.
trans-unit.target: 複寫來源伺服器的名稱。

trans-unit.source: Gets the maximum update sequence number (USN) for which the destination server has accepted changes from the source server.
trans-unit.target: 取得目的伺服器已接受的來源伺服器變更之最大更新序號 (USN)。

trans-unit.source: The maximum update sequence number (USN) for which the destination server has accepted changes from the source server.
trans-unit.target: 目的伺服器已接受的來源伺服器變更之最大更新序號 (USN)。
